room_title: Escape room "Dinner for Two" by Murfreesboro Escape Room in Murfreesboro
review: My fiancé and I went for our anniversary and did the Dinner for Two Room. It was so much fun! This is the 2nd room I have done here and will definitely be checking out what else they have to offer. Great for Date Night or a night our with friends!

room_title: Escape room "Dinner for Two" by Murfreesboro Escape Room in Murfreesboro
review: This was my first time going and it was Awesome, we loved every minute of it. Can’t wait to do another one. Thank you

room_title: Escape room "Dinner for Two" by Murfreesboro Escape Room in Murfreesboro
review: We did "Dinner for Two" and it was so much fun!  This was our first escape room experience and we are so anxious to try another one!  The facility is brand new and very well done.  Excellent staff!
